textBeforeTable: The Orange County (CA) Chapter of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers - Components, Packaging and Manufacturing Technology Society (IEEE-CPMT) is organizing the 2013 Advanced Packaging Materials Symposium and Exhibition.
